Welcome to Texas Mineral Resources



Mission Statement
Texas Mineral Resources believes it is imperative to re-establish the United States as the leader in technology, production and refining of the strategically vital heavy rare earth elements. We intend to be the secure supplier of these elements which are the foundation of our defense and technological infrastructure. Our Round Top deposit is uniquely situated to fill this vital National need.
