			Company Description 


			Texas Mineral Resources Corp. is engaged in the acquisition, exploration and development of mineral properties. It focuses on the development of metallurgical process to concentrate or otherwise extract the metals from the Round Top Projects. The company was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in S...
		


                Texas Mineral Resources Corp. is engaged in the acquisition, exploration and development of mineral properties. It focuses on the development of metallurgical process to concentrate or otherwise extract the metals from the Round Top Projects. The company was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Sierra Blanca, TX.
            




